# Web3Forms access key — powers the contact form email delivery.
# Get a free key at https://web3forms.com (enter the destination inbox,
# e.g. info@firstmanvideos.com, and they email you the access key).
# Copy this file to `.env.local` for local dev, and set the same var in
# the VPS environment before `npm run build` (it is inlined at build time).
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
